{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "semana3-transportista-2026",
    "name": "Semana 3 — Empresa Transportista EFS + S3",
    "description": "# Coleccion alineada con AwsS3Controller (igual al profesor)\n\n**Base URL:** `http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}`\n\n| Metodo | Ruta | Descripcion |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| GET | `/s3/{bucket}/objects` | Listar todos los objetos |\n| GET | `/s3/{bucket}/consulta?fecha=&transportista=` | Consultar guias (actividad) |\n| GET | `/s3/{bucket}/object?...` | Descargar PDF |\n| POST | `/s3/{bucket}/object` | Crear guia (EFS + S3) |\n| PUT | `/s3/{bucket}/object` | Actualizar guia |\n| POST | `/s3/{bucket}/move` | Mover objeto |\n| DELETE | `/s3/{bucket}/object?...` | Eliminar guia |\n\n## Variables\n- `bucket` — nombre de tu bucket S3\n- `ec2_host` — IP elastica EC2\n- `fecha`, `transportista`, `nombreGuia` — modo actividad\n- `s3_key` — modo profesor (pdfs/testEFS1.pdf)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Modo actividad — fecha/transportista",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. POST — Crear guia",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {"key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "Selecciona tu PDF"},
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuia}}", "type": "text"}
              ]
            },
            "url": {"raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object", "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080", "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"]},
            "description": "Key resultante: {{fecha}}/{{transportista}}/{{nombreGuia}}.pdf"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. GET — Consultar por fecha y transportista",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": [
            "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('total >= 1', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().total).to.be.at.least(1));"
          ], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/consulta?fecha={{fecha}}&transportista={{transportista}}",
              "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "consulta"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}"}
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. GET — Descargar guia",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object?fecha={{fecha}}&transportista={{transportista}}&nombreGuia={{nombreGuia}}",
              "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuia}}"}
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. PUT — Actualizar guia",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {"key": "file", "type": "file", "src": []},
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuia}}", "type": "text"}
              ]
            },
            "url": {"raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object", "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080", "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"]}
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5. DELETE — Eliminar guia",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('204 No Content', () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object?fecha={{fecha}}&transportista={{transportista}}&nombreGuia={{nombreGuia}}",
              "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuia}}"}
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Modo profesor — key directa",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. POST — Crear con key",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {"key": "file", "type": "file", "src": []},
                {"key": "key", "value": "{{s3_key}}", "type": "text"}
              ]
            },
            "url": {"raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object", "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080", "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"]}
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. GET — Listar objetos del bucket",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {"raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/objects", "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080", "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "objects"]}
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. GET — Descargar con key",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object?key={{s3_key}}",
              "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"],
              "query": [{"key": "key", "value": "{{s3_key}}"}]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. GET — Consultar historial (fecha=pdfs)",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/consulta?fecha=pdfs",
              "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "consulta"],
              "query": [{"key": "fecha", "value": "pdfs"}]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5. DELETE — Eliminar con key",
          "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["pm.test('204 No Content', () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));"], "type": "text/javascript"}}],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object?key={{s3_key}}",
              "protocol": "http", "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"], "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"],
              "query": [{"key": "key", "value": "{{s3_key}}"}]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {"key": "ec2_host", "value": "52.45.88.121"},
    {"key": "bucket", "value": "tu-bucket-guias", "description": "Nombre de tu bucket S3 (igual que AWS_S3_BUCKET)"},
    {"key": "fecha", "value": "20250604"},
    {"key": "transportista", "value": "TransportesSur"},
    {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "guia001"},
    {"key": "s3_key", "value": "pdfs/testEFS1.pdf"}
  ]
}
